    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> 9th level</em></p>\n<p>You modify your weapon to carry a charge. Over the course of a short rest, you can cast an at-will tech power, channeling it into your weapon. The next time you hit with your weapon, the stored power is released. If the power would require an attack roll, make a tech attack roll. If the power would require a saving throw, the target must make the saving throw as normal. On a hit, or a failure, the target suffers the power's normal effects. </p>",
